ofbestfit.com/news/doja-cat-shares-updated-artwork-for-forthcoming-album-scarlet-following-similarities-to-german-band-chaver">Doja Cat shared an updated album cover</a> –– created by the same artist –– which is notably different, with two pearlescent spiders, instead of the solo red arachnid that originally graced the cover.</p><p> Back in July, Doja Cat <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-loses-180k-instagram-followers-and-deletes-threads-after-lashing-out-at-fans-3473069">deleted her Threads account and lost 180,000 followers on Instagram</a> after criticising her fans in a series of posts. She had <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-calls-out-fans-for-calling-themselves-kittenz-calls-it-creepy-3472563">posted a series of tweets lashing out at her fans</a> , particularly aimed at fan accounts who refer to themselves as &#39;kittenz&#39;.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-posts-selfie-wearing-a-shirt-featuring-an-alleged-neo-nazi-3511009">Doja Cat posts selfie wearing a shirt featuring an alleged Neo-Nazi</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
